This folder implement Serial Peripheral Interface which contain slow clock which is generated from the actual clock, Chip select and MOSI pin

-> There will be the following states
    -> Idle state in which the chip select would be 0
    -> Start transmission state in which the chip select would be low for one clock period
    -> Send data in which the mosi pin is loaded with data and sent
    -> Then end transmission in which the chip select would be 1 once again
    -> Then back to idle state
